    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AdminHomePanel
    The type Admin home panel.
    Amministratore
    An Admin user, it does not add anything from the User class.
    AppController
    The type App controller.
    Bagaglio
    Baggage in the system.
    BagaglioDAO
    The interface Bagaglio dao.
    BagaglioPostgresDAO
    The type Bagaglio postgres dao.
    BaggageDialog
    The Admin Update Baggage dialog.
    BookingDialog
    The Booking dialog that appears when the user is booking a flight.
    DatabaseManager
    The type Database manager.
    FlightDialog
    The Flight dialog.
    FlightDialog.GateWrapper
    This is an internal class (a wrapper class) used to visualize the gate objects in the combobox and to handle the "no gate" ("-- Nessun Gate --") scenario.
    Gate
    Represents an airport's boarding gate.
    GateDAO
    The interface Gate dao.
    GatePostgresDAO
    The type Gate postgres dao.
    LoginPanel
    The Login panel.
    LostBaggageDialog
    The Lost baggage dialog.
    LostBaggageDialog.BagaglioWrapper
    This is an internal class (a wrapper class) used to visualize the baggage objects in the combobox.
    MainApp
    The main class to start the application.
    MainFrame
    The Main frame.
    Prenotazione
    Represents a flight booked by a user.
    PrenotazioneDAO
    The interface Prenotazione dao.
    PrenotazionePostgresDAO
    The type Prenotazione postgres dao.
    RegistrationPanel
    The Registration panel.
    StatoBagaglio
    The enum that indicates the possible states for baggage.
    StatoPrenotazione
    The enum that indicates the possible states of a booking.
    StatoVolo
    The enum that indicates the possible states of a flight.
    UserHomePanel
    The User home panel.
    Utente
    The abstract class for all the users in the system.
    UtenteDAO
    The interface Utente dao.
    UtenteGenerico
    Represent a standard non-admin user.
    UtentePostgresDAO
    The type Utente postgres dao.
    Volo
    The abstract class that represents a flight.
    VoloArrivo
    The class that represents an arriving flight.
    VoloDAO
    The interface Volo dao.
    VoloPartenza
    The class that represents a departing flight.
    VoloPostgresDAO
    The type Volo postgres dao.
